Use the standard library
This is how to largest_prime_factor of n:
   Remember that factor is 2
   Remember that largest is 1

   Do this n times:
      When product of factor and factor is more than n, then:
         Leave the loop
      End when

      Do this n times:
         When remainder of n and factor is not 0, then:
            Leave the loop
         End when
         Remember that largest is factor
         Remember that n is quotient of n and factor
      End do

      Increase factor
   End do

   When n is more than 1, then:
      Remember that largest is n
   End when

   The answer is largest
Now you know

>>> largest_prime_factor of 13195
29
>>> largest_prime_factor of 2048
2
>>> largest_prime_factor of 15
5